    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n`fnamemodify()` does not handle leading slashes correctly, as pointed out by @superatomic firstly in #39724.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nFix it. And harden tests. The last blocker for #39723 (prayge).",
